# Code Owners
#
# This file defines who owns which parts of the codebase.
# When a PR modifies owned files, the owners must be notified.
#
# Lines starting with '#' are comments.
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# Order matters - last matching pattern takes precedence.

# Default owner for everything in the repo
# * @sp-loomis

# Workflow files - must be reviewed by repo owner
/.github/workflows/ @sp-loomis

# Project instructions for Claude - must be reviewed by repo owner
/.claude/CLAUDE.md @sp-loomis
/.claude/settings.json @sp-loomis

# Project instructions for Gemini - must be reviewed by repo owner
/GEMINI.md @sp-loomis

# Code ownership definitions - must be reviewed by repo owner
/CODEOWNERS @sp-loomis

# Example: Add your own code ownership patterns below
